<li id="cite_note-59"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-59">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation web"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/styleguide/page/0,,184835,00.html">"Guardian Style Guide"</a>. The Guardian<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/styleguide/page/0,,184835,00.html">http://www.guardian.co.uk/styleguide/page/0,,184835,00.html</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved 2008-12-03</span>. "different from or to, not different than"</span></span></li>
